cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.AI. 

The paper presents a method for improving the efficiency of RANSAC, a commonly used algorithm in computer vision and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions applications in camera localization (cs.RO - Robotics), and uses machine learning techniques such as the generalized Hough transform (cs.LG - Machine Learning). The paper also discusses adapting the "Random Grids" range-search technique (cs.GR - Graphics) and achieving state-of-the-art results (cs.AI - Artificial Intelligence).
